<bibRefCitation author="Zhang, XM" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" pagination="39 - 46" title="Review of the leafhopper genus Taperus Li &amp; Wang (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Evacanthinae) from China, with description of three new species." volume="2721" year="2010">Zhang et al. (2010)</bibRefCitation>
.
